BEGIN
 	DECLARE vRESPONSE BOOLEAN;
     DECLARE vMUST_CHECK VARCHAR(10);
  	select COALESCE(THE_VALUE, 'false') INTO vMUST_CHECK
 	from EXP_SETTING
 	where CATEGORY = 'option' AND SETTING = 'CARRIER_INSUFFCIENT_INS';
     IF vMUST_CHECK = 'false' THEN
 		SET vRESPONSE = true;
     ELSE
 		-- Check required insurance
 		SELECT COUNT(*) = 0 INTO vRESPONSE
 		FROM EXP_LOAD l, EXP_SHIPMENT s, EXP_CLIENT c, EXP_CARRIER_INS v
 		WHERE l.LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN
         AND v.CARRIER_CODE = CARRIER_IN
 		AND l.LOAD_CODE = s.LOAD_CODE
 		AND s.BILLTO_CLIENT_CODE = c.CLIENT_CODE
 		AND (
 			v.GENERAL_LIAB_INS < COALESCE(c.GENERAL_LIAB_INS,0) *
 				CONVERT_RATE( get_asof(s.SHIPMENT_CODE), c.CURRENCY_CODE, v.CURRENCY_CODE)
 			OR v.AUTO_LIAB_INS < COALESCE(c.AUTO_LIAB_INS,0) *
 				CONVERT_RATE( get_asof(s.SHIPMENT_CODE), c.CURRENCY_CODE, v.CURRENCY_CODE)
 			OR v.CARGO_LIAB_INS < COALESCE(c.CARGO_LIAB_INS,0) *
 				CONVERT_RATE( get_asof(s.SHIPMENT_CODE), c.CURRENCY_CODE, v.CURRENCY_CODE)
 			OR COALESCE(c.GENERAL_LIAB_INS,0) > 0 AND v.GENERAL_DAYS <= 0
 			OR COALESCE(c.AUTO_LIAB_INS,0) > 0 AND v.AUTO_DAYS <= 0
 			OR COALESCE(c.CARGO_LIAB_INS,0) > 0 AND v.CARGO_DAYS <= 0
 		);
     END IF;
 RETURN vRESPONSE;
 END

BEGIN
	DECLARE vACTUAL_DELIVERY DATE;
	DECLARE vACTUAL_DEPART DATE;
    DECLARE vPICKUP_DATE DATE; 
    DECLARE vDELIVER_DATE DATE;
    
	DECLARE vTRANS_DATE VARCHAR(255);
	DECLARE vUSE_DUE_DATE VARCHAR(255);
	DECLARE vCONS_TRANS_DATE VARCHAR(255);
	DECLARE vCONSOLIDATE VARCHAR(255);
    DECLARE vSHIPMENT int;
    DECLARE vRESULT DATE;
    DECLARE vIS_CONSOLIDATED VARCHAR(10);
		
	-- Which date to use (shipped/delivered)
	select THE_VALUE INTO vTRANS_DATE
	from EXP_SETTING 
	where CATEGORY = 'api' AND SETTING = 'QUICKBOOKS_TRANSACTION_DATE'
	order by SETTING_CODE DESC
    LIMIT 1;
    
	-- Which date to use (earliest/parent)
	select THE_VALUE INTO vCONS_TRANS_DATE
	from EXP_SETTING 
	where CATEGORY = 'api' AND SETTING = 'CONSOLIDATED_TRANSACTION_DATE'
	order by SETTING_CODE DESC
    LIMIT 1;
    
	-- Use the due date?
	select THE_VALUE INTO vUSE_DUE_DATE
	from EXP_SETTING 
	where CATEGORY = 'option' AND SETTING = 'USE_DUE_DATE_OVER_ACTUAL'
	order by SETTING_CODE DESC
    LIMIT 1;
    
	-- Consolidate shipments enabled?
	select THE_VALUE INTO vCONSOLIDATE
	from EXP_SETTING 
	where CATEGORY = 'option' AND SETTING = 'CONSOLIDATE_SHIPMENTS'
	order by SETTING_CODE DESC
    LIMIT 1;
    
    -- Is this shipment consolidated?
    SELECT CASE WHEN CONSOLIDATE_NUM IS NOT NULL THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END
    INTO vIS_CONSOLIDATED
	FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
	WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = SHIPMENT_IN;
    
    -- deal with consolidated shipments here
    IF vCONSOLIDATE = 'true' AND vIS_CONSOLIDATED = 'true' THEN
		SELECT CONSOLIDATE_NUM INTO vSHIPMENT
        FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
        WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = SHIPMENT_IN;

 	    -- Shipment pickup by/deliver by
	    SELECT CASE WHEN vCONS_TRANS_DATE = 'earliest' THEN
				MIN(PICKUP_DATE) ELSE MAX(PICKUP_DATE)
				END AS PICKUP_DATE,
				CASE WHEN vCONS_TRANS_DATE = 'earliest' THEN
				MIN(DELIVER_DATE) ELSE MAX(DELIVER_DATE)
				END AS DELIVER_DATE
	    INTO vPICKUP_DATE, vDELIVER_DATE
	    FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
	    WHERE CONSOLIDATE_NUM = vSHIPMENT
	    LIMIT 1;
	    
	    IF vTRANS_DATE = 'delivered' THEN
			-- Actual delivery date
			SELECT DATE(CASE WHEN vCONS_TRANS_DATE = 'earliest' THEN
				MIN(ACTUAL_DEPART) ELSE MAX(ACTUAL_DEPART)
				END) AS ACTUAL_DELIVERY INTO vACTUAL_DELIVERY
			FROM EXP_STOP, EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE COALESCE(CONSOLIDATE_NUM, SHIPMENT_CODE) = vSHIPMENT
            AND SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_CODE
			AND STOP_TYPE IN ('drop', 'dropdock')
		    LIMIT 1;
	    
			IF vUSE_DUE_DATE = 'true' THEN
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vDELIVER_DATE,vACTUAL_DELIVERY,CURRENT_DATE);
			ELSE
 				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vACTUAL_DELIVERY,vDELIVER_DATE,CURRENT_DATE);
			END IF;
		ELSE
			-- Actual pickup date
			SELECT DATE(CASE WHEN vCONS_TRANS_DATE = 'earliest' THEN
				MIN(ACTUAL_DEPART) ELSE MAX(ACTUAL_DEPART)
				END) AS ACTUAL_DEPART INTO vACTUAL_DEPART
			FROM EXP_STOP, EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE COALESCE(CONSOLIDATE_NUM, SHIPMENT_CODE) = vSHIPMENT
            AND SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_CODE
			AND STOP_TYPE IN ('pick', 'pickdock')
		    LIMIT 1;
	    
			IF vUSE_DUE_DATE = 'true' THEN
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vPICKUP_DATE,vACTUAL_DEPART,CURRENT_DATE);
            ELSE
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vACTUAL_DEPART,vPICKUP_DATE,CURRENT_DATE);
            END IF;
	   END IF;
    ELSE
    	-- Deal with single shipment

	    -- Shipment pickup by/deliver by
	    SELECT PICKUP_DATE, DELIVER_DATE
	    INTO vPICKUP_DATE, vDELIVER_DATE
	    FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
	    WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = SHIPMENT_IN
	    LIMIT 1;
	    
	    IF vTRANS_DATE = 'delivered' THEN
			-- Actual delivery date
			SELECT DATE(ACTUAL_DEPART) AS ACTUAL_DELIVERY INTO vACTUAL_DELIVERY
			FROM EXP_STOP
			WHERE SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_IN
			AND STOP_TYPE IN ('drop', 'dropdock')
		    LIMIT 1;
	    
			IF vUSE_DUE_DATE = 'true' THEN
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vDELIVER_DATE,vACTUAL_DELIVERY,CURRENT_DATE);
            ELSE
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vACTUAL_DELIVERY,vDELIVER_DATE,CURRENT_DATE);
            END IF;
		ELSE
			-- Actual pickup date
			SELECT DATE(ACTUAL_DEPART) AS ACTUAL_DEPART INTO vACTUAL_DEPART
			FROM EXP_STOP
			WHERE SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_IN
			AND STOP_TYPE IN ('pick', 'pickdock')
		    LIMIT 1;
	    
			IF vUSE_DUE_DATE = 'true' THEN
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vPICKUP_DATE,vACTUAL_DEPART,CURRENT_DATE);
            ELSE
				-- Pick first non-null date, or null
				SET vRESULT = COALESCE(vACTUAL_DEPART,vPICKUP_DATE,CURRENT_DATE);
            END IF;
	   END IF;
    END IF;

RETURN vRESULT;
END

BEGIN
	DECLARE vEMAIL varchar(128);
    
	SELECT CASE WHEN SHIPMENTS = 1 THEN
		COALESCE(ADDRESS1, ADDRESS2, '')
	ELSE '' END AS EMAIL
    INTO vEMAIL
	
	FROM (
	SELECT SOURCE_CODE, SOURCE_TYPE,
		CASE WHEN SOURCE_TYPE = 'shipment' THEN 1
		ELSE
			(SELECT COUNT(*)
			FROM EXP_LOAD, EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE = SOURCE_CODE
			AND EXP_SHIPMENT.LOAD_CODE = EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE)
		END AS SHIPMENTS,
		
		CASE WHEN SOURCE_TYPE = 'shipment' THEN
			(SELECT BILLTO_EMAIL FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = SOURCE_CODE
			AND COALESCE(BILLTO_EMAIL,'') <> '')
		ELSE
			(SELECT BILLTO_EMAIL
			FROM EXP_SHIPMENT, EXP_LOAD
			WHERE EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE = SOURCE_CODE
			AND EXP_SHIPMENT.LOAD_CODE = EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE
			AND COALESCE(BILLTO_EMAIL,'') <> ''
			LIMIT 1)
		END AS ADDRESS1,
		
		CASE WHEN SOURCE_TYPE = 'shipment' THEN
			(SELECT EMAIL
			FROM EXP_SHIPMENT, EXP_CONTACT_INFO
			WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = SOURCE_CODE
			AND CONTACT_CODE = BILLTO_CLIENT_CODE
			AND CONTACT_SOURCE = 'client'
			AND CONTACT_TYPE = 'bill_to'
			AND COALESCE(EMAIL,'') <> ''
			LIMIT 1)
		ELSE
			(SELECT EMAIL
			FROM EXP_LOAD, EXP_SHIPMENT, EXP_CONTACT_INFO
			WHERE EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE = SOURCE_CODE
			AND EXP_SHIPMENT.LOAD_CODE = EXP_LOAD.LOAD_CODE
			AND CONTACT_CODE = BILLTO_CLIENT_CODE
			AND CONTACT_SOURCE = 'client'
			AND CONTACT_TYPE = 'bill_to'
			AND COALESCE(EMAIL,'') <> ''
			LIMIT 1)
		END AS ADDRESS2
	
	FROM EXP_ATTACHMENT
	WHERE ATTACHMENT_CODE = ATTACHMENT_IN
	AND SOURCE_TYPE IN ('shipment', 'load')
	) X;
RETURN vEMAIL;
END

BEGIN

    DECLARE vLOGO VARCHAR(128);

 	select COALESCE(THE_VALUE, 'false') INTO vMULTI_COMPANY
	from EXP_SETTING 
	where CATEGORY = 'option' AND SETTING = 'MULTI_COMPANY';
    
    IF vMULTI_COMPANY = 'true' THEN
		-- Make sure we have Logo items
		SELECT COALESCE(ITEM_CODE,0) INTO vLOGOITEM
        FROM EXP_ITEM_LIST 
		WHERE ITEM_TYPE = 'Attachment type' AND ITEM = 'Logo';
        IF vLOGOITEM = 0 THEN
			INSERT INTO EXP_ITEM_LIST( ITEM_TYPE, ITEM, CREATED_BY, CREATED_DATE )
				VALUES( 'Attachment type', 'Logo', 0, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP );
        END IF;

		-- Office, Company, Setting, or NONE
		SELECT COALESCE(
			(SELECT A.STORED_AS
				FROM EXP_ATTACHMENT A
				WHERE A.SOURCE_TYPE = 'office'
                AND A.SOURCE_CODE = OFFICE_IN
                AND A.FILE_TYPE = (SELECT ITEM_CODE FROM EXP_ITEM_LIST
					WHERE ITEM_TYPE = 'Attachment type' AND ITEM = 'Logo'
                    LIMIT 1)),
			(SELECT A.STORED_AS
				FROM EXP_ATTACHMENT A, EXP_OFFICE O
				WHERE O.OFFICE_CODE = OFFICE_IN
                AND A.SOURCE_CODE = O.COMPANY_CODE
                AND A.SOURCE_TYPE = 'company'
                AND A.FILE_TYPE = (SELECT ITEM_CODE FROM EXP_ITEM_LIST
					WHERE ITEM_TYPE = 'Attachment type' AND ITEM = 'Logo'
                    LIMIT 1)), 
			(select THE_VALUE
				from EXP_SETTING 
				where CATEGORY = 'company' AND SETTING = 'LOGO'
				AND THE_VALUE <> ''),
			'NONE' ) INTO vLOGO;	
	ELSE
		select COALESCE(THE_VALUE, 'NONE') INTO vLOGO
		from EXP_SETTING 
		where CATEGORY = 'company' AND SETTING = 'LOGO';
    END IF;

RETURN vLOGO;
END

 	select SHIPMENT INTO vSHIPMENT
	from EXP_STOP 
	where LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN

    ORDER BY SEQUENCE_NO
    LIMIT 1;
    
	SELECT CASE WHEN PICKDROP_IN = 'pick' THEN

		ELSE

            WHERE EXP_STOP.SHIPMENT = EXP_SHIPMENT.SHIPMENT_CODE
            AND STOP_TYPE IN ('pick', 'pickdock') LIMIT 1)

BEGIN
    DECLARE vEXPENSE DOUBLE;

	SELECT ROUND(SUM(CONVERT_LOAD_TO_HOME( LOAD_CODE, COST )),2) CONVERTED
    INTO vEXPENSE
	
	FROM (SELECT LOAD_CODE,
	CASE WHEN CARRIER > 0 THEN 
		ROUND(COALESCE(CARRIER_BASE,0) + COALESCE(CARRIER_FSC,0) +
			COALESCE(CARRIER_HANDLING, 0),2)
	ELSE
		ROUND(COALESCE((SELECT M.TOTAL_TRIP_PAY FROM EXP_LOAD_PAY_MASTER M
			WHERE M.LOAD_ID=L.LOAD_CODE
            LIMIT 1),0),2) 
	END AS COST
	        
	FROM EXP_LOAD L
	WHERE LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN) M;


RETURN vEXPENSE;
END

BEGIN
    DECLARE vREVENUE DOUBLE;

	SELECT ROUND(SUM(CONVERT_TO_HOME( U.SHIPMENT_CODE,
		ROUND(U.SUBTOTAL, 2) )),2) CONVERTED
	INTO vREVENUE
	FROM (SELECT S.SHIPMENT_CODE, S.SUBTOTAL,
		CASE WHEN CLIENT_EXEMPT = 1 OR SHIPMENT_EXEMPT = 1 OR t.APPLICABLE_TAX IS NULL THEN 0
		WHEN t.APPLICABLE_TAX = 'GST' THEN t.GST_RATE
		WHEN t.APPLICABLE_TAX = 'HST' THEN t.HST_RATE
		WHEN t.APPLICABLE_TAX = 'GST+QST' THEN 
		CASE WHEN S.SHIPPER_STATE = S.CONS_STATE THEN t.GST_RATE + t.QST_RATE
		ELSE t.GST_RATE END
		END AS RATE
		
		FROM (SELECT SHIPMENT_CODE, SHIPPER_STATE, SHIPPER_COUNTRY,
			CONS_STATE, CONS_COUNTRY,
			SHIPMENT_HOME_CURRENCY( SHIPMENT_CODE ) AS HOME_CURRENCY,
	    	COALESCE((SELECT TOTAL FROM EXP_CLIENT_BILLING
			    WHERE SHIPMENT_ID = EXP_SHIPMENT.SHIPMENT_CODE LIMIT 1),0) AS SUBTOTAL,
			SHIPMENT_CURRENCY( SHIPMENT_CODE ) AS CURRENCY,
			(SELECT CDN_TAX_EXEMPT FROM EXP_CLIENT
				WHERE CLIENT_CODE = EXP_SHIPMENT.BILLTO_CLIENT_CODE) AS CLIENT_EXEMPT,
			CDN_TAX_EXEMPT AS SHIPMENT_EXEMPT
           
	    	FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN ) S
		left join exp_canada_tax t
		on t.PROVINCE = s.CONS_STATE
        AND s.shipper_country = 'Canada'
		AND s.cons_country = 'Canada') U;

RETURN vREVENUE;
END

BEGIN
DECLARE vDUE datetime;

SELECT 
    cast(DUE as datetime)
INTO vDUE FROM
    (SELECT 
        SHIPMENT,
            concat_ws(' ', coalesce(DELIVER_DATE, current_date),
				(case
					when DELIVER_TIME_OPTION = 'ASAP' then '23:59'
					when coalesce(DELIVER_TIME1, '') = '' then '00:00'
					else concat_ws(':', substr(DELIVER_TIME1, 1, 2), substr(DELIVER_TIME1, 3, 2))
				end)) AS DUE,
            SEQUENCE_NO
    FROM
        EXP_STOP, EXP_SHIPMENT
    WHERE
        EXP_STOP.LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN
            AND STOP_TYPE IN ('drop' , 'dropdock')
            AND EXP_STOP.CURRENT_STATUS = (SELECT 
                STATUS_CODES_CODE
            FROM
                EXP_STATUS_CODES
            WHERE
                SOURCE_TYPE = 'stop' AND BEHAVIOR = 'entry')
            AND SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_CODE
	ORDER BY SEQUENCE_NO ASC
	LIMIT 1) X;

RETURN vDUE;
END

BEGIN
DECLARE vDUE datetime;

SET session time_zone = '-5:00'; 

SELECT 
    cast(DUE as datetime)
INTO vDUE FROM
    (SELECT 
        SHIPMENT,
            case when DUE_DATE is null then DATE_ADD(curdate(), INTERVAL 1 YEAR)
            else
            concat_ws(' ', DUE_DATE, (case
                when TIME_OPTION IN ('ASAP', 'FCFS') then '23:59'
                when coalesce(DUE_TIME, '') = '' then '00:00'
                else concat_ws(':', substr(DUE_TIME, 1, 2), substr(DUE_TIME, 3, 2))
            end)) end AS DUE,
            SEQUENCE_NO,
            STOP_TYPE
    FROM
        (SELECT 
        SHIPMENT,
            CASE
                when STOP_TYPE in ('pick' , 'pickdock') then PICKUP_DATE
                else DELIVER_DATE
            end AS DUE_DATE,
            CASE
                when STOP_TYPE in ('pick' , 'pickdock') then PICKUP_TIME1
                else DELIVER_TIME1
            end AS DUE_TIME,
            CASE
                when STOP_TYPE in ('pick' , 'pickdock') then PICKUP_TIME_OPTION
                else DELIVER_TIME_OPTION
            end AS TIME_OPTION,
            SEQUENCE_NO,
            STOP_TYPE
    FROM
        EXP_STOP, EXP_SHIPMENT
    WHERE
        EXP_STOP.LOAD_CODE = LOAD_IN
            AND STOP_TYPE IN ('pick' , 'drop', 'pickdock', 'dropdock')
            AND EXP_STOP.CURRENT_STATUS = (SELECT 
                STATUS_CODES_CODE
            FROM
                EXP_STATUS_CODES
            WHERE
                SOURCE_TYPE = 'stop' AND BEHAVIOR = 'entry')
            AND SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_CODE) a
    order by 3 asc
    limit 1) X;


RETURN vDUE;
END

begin

    DECLARE vLAT DOUBLE;
    DECLARE vLON DOUBLE;

    IF( NEW.CURRENT_STATUS <> OLD.CURRENT_STATUS ) THEN
		SELECT SHIPMENT
		INTO CURR_SHIPMENT
		FROM EXP_STOP
		WHERE NEW.LOAD_CODE = EXP_STOP.LOAD_CODE
		AND NEW.CURRENT_STOP = EXP_STOP.SEQUENCE_NO;
        
        SELECT CASE WHEN STOP_TYPE = 'pick' THEN SHIPPER_LAT
		WHEN STOP_TYPE = 'drop' THEN CONS_LAT
		ELSE S.STOP_LAT END AS LAT,
		CASE WHEN STOP_TYPE = 'pick' THEN SHIPPER_LON
		WHEN STOP_TYPE = 'drop' THEN CONS_LON
		ELSE S.STOP_LON END AS LON
        INTO vLAT, vLON
		FROM EXP_STOP S
        LEFT JOIN EXP_SHIPMENT SH
        ON S.SHIPMENT = SH.SHIPMENT_CODE
		WHERE NEW.LOAD_CODE = S.LOAD_CODE
		AND NEW.CURRENT_STOP = S.SEQUENCE_NO
        AND (SELECT BEHAVIOR
			FROM EXP_STATUS_CODES S
			WHERE NEW.CURRENT_STATUS = S.STATUS_CODES_CODE) IN ('arrive cons', 'arrrecdock',
				'arrive shipper','arrshdock','arrive stop','depart cons','deprecdock',
				'depart shipper', 'depshdock', 'depart stop','dispatch');

		INSERT INTO `EXP_STATUS` (ORDER_CODE, SOURCE_TYPE, STATUS_STATE, ZONE, COMMENTS, LAT, LON,
			STATUS_STOP, SHIPMENT, CREATED_DATE, CREATED_BY)
		values(NEW.LOAD_CODE, 'load', NEW.CURRENT_STATUS, NEW.CURRENT_ZONE,
			concat('STOP=',NEW.CURRENT_STOP,' SHIPMENT=',CURR_SHIPMENT), vLAT, vLON,
            NEW.CURRENT_STOP, CURR_SHIPMENT, NEW.CHANGED_DATE, NEW.CHANGED_BY);

BEGIN
	DECLARE vCLIENT_NAME VARCHAR(128);
	DECLARE vCLIENT_CODE_MATCH INT(11);
	
	IF( NEW.CURRENT_STATUS <> OLD.CURRENT_STATUS AND NEW.STOP_TYPE <> 'stop') THEN
		IF( NEW.STOP_TYPE = 'pick' ) THEN
		
			SELECT SHIPPER_NAME
			INTO vCLIENT_NAME
			FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = NEW.SHIPMENT;
			
			SELECT CLIENT_CODE
			INTO vCLIENT_CODE_MATCH
			FROM EXP_CLIENT
			WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_CODE = COALESCE( 
				(SELECT CLIENT_CODE
				FROM EXP_CLIENT
				WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_NAME = vCLIENT_NAME
				LIMIT 1), (SELECT CONTACT_CODE
				FROM EXP_CONTACT_INFO
				WHERE CONTACT_SOURCE = 'client'
				AND CONTACT_TYPE = 'shipper'
				AND LABEL = vCLIENT_NAME
				LIMIT 1) );
							
			UPDATE EXP_CLIENT
			SET PALLET_COUNT = COALESCE(PALLET_COUNT, 0) - (SELECT PALLETS
				FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
				WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = NEW.SHIPMENT)
			WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_CODE = vCLIENT_CODE_MATCH
			AND EXP_CLIENT.TRACK_PALLETS = TRUE;

		ELSEIF ( NEW.STOP_TYPE = 'drop' ) THEN

			SELECT CONS_NAME
			INTO vCLIENT_NAME
			FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
			WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = NEW.SHIPMENT;

			SELECT CLIENT_CODE
			INTO vCLIENT_CODE_MATCH
			FROM EXP_CLIENT
			WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_CODE = COALESCE( 
				(SELECT CLIENT_CODE
				FROM EXP_CLIENT
				WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_NAME = vCLIENT_NAME
				LIMIT 1), (SELECT CONTACT_CODE
				FROM EXP_CONTACT_INFO
				WHERE CONTACT_SOURCE = 'client'
				AND CONTACT_TYPE = 'consignee'
				AND LABEL = vCLIENT_NAME
				LIMIT 1) );
							
			UPDATE EXP_CLIENT
			SET PALLET_COUNT = COALESCE(PALLET_COUNT, 0) + (SELECT PALLETS
				FROM EXP_SHIPMENT
				WHERE SHIPMENT_CODE = NEW.SHIPMENT)
			WHERE EXP_CLIENT.CLIENT_CODE = vCLIENT_CODE_MATCH
			AND EXP_CLIENT.TRACK_PALLETS = TRUE;
            
            -- 2.03 UPDATE EXP_SHIPMENT.ACTUAL_DELIVERY 
            IF( NEW.CURRENT_STATUS = (SELECT STATUS_CODES_CODE FROM EXP_STATUS_CODES
				WHERE SOURCE_TYPE = 'stop' AND STATUS_STATE = 'Dropped') ) THEN
                UPDATE EXP_SHIPMENT
                SET ACTUAL_DELIVERY = COALESCE(NEW.ACTUAL_DEPART, NEW.CHANGED_DATE)
                WHERE NEW.SHIPMENT = SHIPMENT_CODE;
			END IF;

		END IF;
	END IF;
END
